      <description><![CDATA[<div>
        
<p>Install Iredmail</p>

<p>See the Iredmail documentation <a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20141115122245/&lt;a%20href=" http:>http:/<wbr></wbr>/<wbr></wbr>www.iredmail.org:80/<wbr></wbr>install_iredmail_on_ubuntu.html</a>"&gt;<a href="http://www.iredmail.org/install">http:/<wbr></wbr>/<wbr></wbr>www.iredmail.org/<wbr></wbr>install</a><em>iredmail</em>on_ubuntu.html for more details</p>

<p>First install bzip2</p>

<p><em>apt-get install bzip2</em></p>

<p>Edit first line of /etc/hosts</p>

<p><em>nano /etc/hosts</em></p>

<p>To read like the following</p>
<blockquote>
<p>127.0.0.1       mail.theojones.name localhost mail</p>

<p> </p>
</blockquote>
<p>Download Ired Mail</p>

<p>wget <a href="https://bitbucket.org/zhb/iredmail/downloads/iRedMail-0.8.5.tar.bz2"></a><a href="https://bitbucket.org/zhb/iredmail/downloads/iRedMail-0.8.5.tar.bz2">https:/<wbr></wbr>/<wbr></wbr>bitbucket.org/<wbr></wbr>zhb/<wbr></wbr>iredmail/<wbr></wbr>downloads/<wbr></wbr>iRedMail-0.8.5.tar.bz2</a></p>

<p>Untar Ired mail.</p>

<p>tar xjf iRedMail-0.8.5.tar.bz2</p>

<p><strong>Add forwarding</strong></p>

<p>Go to <a href="https://mail.theojones.name/phpldapadmin/htdocs/cmd.php"></a><a href="https://mail.theojones.name/phpldapadmin/htdocs/cmd.php">https:/<wbr></wbr>/<wbr></wbr>mail.theojones.name/<wbr></wbr>phpldapadmin/<wbr></wbr>htdocs/<wbr></wbr>cmd.php</a></p>
